name: BRAVE CustomMix
description:
Since I've learned about how to merge models and inspired by the results from NostalRealMix, decided to try to make my own just for a little fun.

So I've decided to merge BRA(Beautiful Realistic Asians) model with BB-MIX-EVE. The results are not bad.

Parameters I use:

  • DPM++SDE Karras

  • Sampling steps: 20

  • R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B

  • Denoising Strengh: 0.45

  • Hire steps: 10

  • Upscale: 2

  • Resolution: 512x768

  • CFG Scale: 7

  • Clip Skip: 1 or 2

modelVersions.name: BRAVE CustomMix v2
modelVersions.description:
Added a few models to the merge and the quality seems to improve a little. I tried some prompts combinations and LoRAS and get interesting images and check the quality. However I'm still lost about how to improve this besides basic merging with some models.

The model is pruned so the size is lower than the previous version.
